title: Shahs: Voy Meets World
description:
After a one night stand with Sara's brother Sam, Destiney faces the scrutiny of the group on this week's Shah's of Sunset. Plus, it's a quadruple dose of filler activities: DIY pottery, cat coffee, dance class, and a cooking competition!
